.pdf"}, {"verified_claim": {"claim": {"id": "c3245cd1", "text": "All companies processing EU personal data must appoint a Data Protection Officer without exception", "normalized": "Every organization handling European Union personal data is required to designate a Data Protection Officer, regardless of the size or nature of the company", "claim_type": "legal", "stakes": "critical", "span_start": 190, "span_end": 258}, "status": "verified", "confidence": 0.95, "supporting_docs": [{"doc_id": "4217c1558e88", "source": "4444444444444444.pdf", "excerpt": "m/uploads/statutory/pdf/\nrelated-party-transaction-policy.pdf\n8. DISCLOSURE OF INTERNAL FINANCIAL CONTROLS:\nThe Internal Financial Controls followed by the \nCompany are adequate and commensurate with \nthe size and nature of the business and were \noperating effectively during the year under review. I", "relevance_score": 0.371, "rerank_score": -8.630407333374023}, {"doc_id": "eb7aa487a220", "source": "Population-physiologically-based-modeling-of-pirlimycin-_2020_Journal-of-Dai.pdf", "excerpt": "eeting of the Joint FAO/WHO Expert Committee on \nFood Additives. Food and Agriculture Organization of the United \nNations, Rome, Italy. Henri, J., A.-M. Jacques, P. Sanders, A. Chevance, and M. Laurentie. \n2017. The present and future of withdrawal period calculations for \nmilk in the European Union", "relevance_score": 0.3662, "rerank_score": -9.722006797790527}, {"doc_id": "5106645e9211", "source": "05_17-1-2023-N-Manoharan_Niharika-Singh-Rana.pdf", "excerpt": "him in pursuance of a warrant or order \nof competent authority\u2019. Interestingly, such protection is available \n\u2018notwithstanding any defect in the jurisdiction of the authority which \nissued such warrant or order\u2019.36\nIt should be noted that protection against arrest is available to all the \narmed forc", "relevance_score": 0.3792, "rerank_score": -10.150867462158203}], "contradiction_reason": null, "verification_reasoning": "Every organization handling European Union personal data is required to designate a Data Protection Officer if they are a public authority or their core activities require regular and systematic monitoring of data subjects on a large scale or consist of processing special categories of data.", "key_evidence": "According to Article 37 of the GDPR, 'the controller and the processor shall designate a data protection officer in any case where: (a) the processing is carried out by a public authority or body; (b) the core activities of the controller or the processor consist of processing operations which require regular and systematic monitoring of data subjects on a large scale; or (c) the core activities of the controller or the processor consist of processing special categories of data on a large scale' (<https://gdpr-info.eu/art-37-gdpr/>)."}, "action": "annotate", "annotation": "VERIFIED (confidence 0.95) \u2014 Source: 4444444444444444.pdf, Population-physiologically-based-modeling-of-pirlimycin-_2020_Journal-of-Dai.pdf"}], "retrieval_metadata": [{"claim_id": "25c421c7", "query_variants": ["The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) was enacted on the 1st of June, 2019", "'General Data Protection Regulation' enactment date", "GDPR effective date in EU", "When was the General Data Protection Regulation officially implemented?"], "total_retrieved": 11, "total_after_rerank": 3, "cache_hit": false, "ensemble_used": false}, {"claim_id": "1761e7da", "query_variants": ["According to the GDPR, data breaches should be reported to regulatory bodies within 24 hours after detection", "GDPR data breach reporting timeframe", "What is the required time for reporting a data breach according to GDPR?", "How long does a company have to report a data breach under GDPR?"], "total_retrieved": 19, "total_after_rerank": 3, "cache_hit": false, "ensemble_used": false}, {"claim_id": "2d38a236", "query_variants": ["The highest fine under the GDPR can be either 10 million EUR or 2% of a company's worldwide an