ank_score": null}, {"doc_id": "7077c5c100a1", "source": "MILK-Symposium-review--The-importance-of-milk-and-dairy-food_2020_Journal-of.pdf", "excerpt": "ing to \nreduced mobility, disability, and lower quality of life. A \nlesser-known outcome of reduced muscle mass and pos-\nsibly associated reduced exercise ability is the increased \nrisk of metabolic diseases, type 2 diabetes in particular \n(Hunter et al., 2019). Based on general population studies, ", "relevance_score": 0.4, "rerank_score": null}, {"doc_id": "7077c5c100a1", "source": "MILK-Symposium-review--The-importance-of-milk-and-dairy-food_2020_Journal-of.pdf", "excerpt": "ave major \nnegative effects on quality of life and independence. It \nis also now appreciated that both reduced muscle mass \nand reduced mobility can increase the risk of type 2 \ndiabetes, which further reduces healthy and quality life \nspan (Hunter et al., 2019). In middle and later life, cardiovasc", "relevance_score": 0.3793, "rerank_score": null}], "contradiction_reason": null, "verification_reasoning": "The World Health Organization states that about 500 million individuals worldwide are currently affected by diabetes.", "key_evidence": "Approximately 650 million adults and over 340 million children were overweight or obese in 2016, which can lead to diabetes (Source 5)"}, "action": "annotate", "annotation": "VERIFIED (confidence 0.95) \u2014 Source: Lactococcus-chungangensis-CAU-28-alleviates-diet-induced-obe_2020_Journal-of.pdf, MILK-Symposium-review--The-importance-of-milk-and-dairy-food_2020_Journal-of.pdf"}, {"verified_claim": {"claim": {"id": "0d48f8fc", "text": "Ibuprofen is safe to use throughout all trimesters of pregnancy", "normalized": "The use of Ibuprofen is considered safe during all stages of pregnancy", "claim_type": "medical", "stakes": "critical", "span_start": 130, "span_end": 164}, "status": "unverifiable", "confidence": 0.3, "supporting_docs": [{"doc_id": "5e4759c80917", "source": "111111111.pdf", "excerpt":