an \u00a350 million towards research. On 16 April 2020, it was reported that the UK would have first access to the Oxford v", "relevance_score": 0.7168, "rerank_score": 2.9008193016052246}], "contradiction_reason": null, "verification_reasoning": "The source directly states that COVID-19 vaccines became available under emergency use in December 2020, and the Pfizer-BioNTech vaccine was one of the first to be authorized.", "key_evidence": "COVID-19 vaccines became available under emergency use in December 2020"}, "action": "flag", "annotation": "FLAGGED \u2014 Low confidence (0.88, LEGAL threshold 0.93): The source directly states that COVID-19 vaccines became available under emergency use in December 2020, and the Pfizer-"}], "retrieval_metadata": [{"claim_id": "d40127c1", "query_variants": ["Alexander Fleming discovered penicillin in 1928.", "Alexander Fleming penicillin discovery 1928", "History of penicillin discovery date"], "total_retrieved": 18, "total_after_rerank": 5, "cache_hit": false, "ensemble_used": false}, {"claim_id": "98264a7f", "query_variants": ["The WHO states that approximately 500 million people worldwide have diabetes.", "WHO diabetes prevalence statistics 2023", "Global diabetes prevalence numbers according to World Health Organization"], "total_retrieved": 29, "total_after_rerank": 5, "cache_hit": false, "ensemble_used": false}, {"claim_id": "fb252f1f", "query_variants": ["Ibuprofen is safe to use throughout all trimesters of pregnancy.", "Ibuprofen safety during pregnancy trimesters", "Pregnancy trimester use of ibuprofen risks and benefits"], "total_retrieved": 26, "total_after_rerank": 5, "cache_hit": false, "ensemble_used": false}, {"claim_id": "109b7221", "query_variants": ["The Pfizer-BioNTech vaccine was the first COVID-19 vaccine authorised for emergency use in December 2020.", "Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 vaccine emergency use authorization December 2020", "First COVID-19 vaccine approved for emergency use by FDA in 2020"], "total_retri